 anyone prove otherwise.<br><br>To sum it up, there is old raid content that a knight is not viable to tank and won't be ever be able to just as there is content you can not solo and more and likley you won't be able to solo. Get us to it.<br><br>Grouping is 6 people. Soloing is 1 Raiding is usually 24 plus....the difference is simple power. Grouping does mean more then 1 so soloing has nothing to do with grouping. With the power increase from 6 + I don't consider raiding grouping...symantics or not. Not only becuase of the power gain but the opening of different roles and other class focuses; a relatively different pyramid with a different set of rules. SO again raiding does not equal grouping.<br></span></div>
